    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) supported by validation evidence. Assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
